msgctxt "dn34:93.7"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn34:93.8"
msgid "nissaraṇaṃ hetaṃ, āvuso, aratiyā, yadidaṃ muditācetovimuttī’ti."
msgstr ""
"For it is the heart’s release by rejoicing that is the escape from "
"negativity.’"

msgctxt "dn34:93.9"
msgid "(7.3)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="86"></a>
msgctxt "dn34:94.1"
msgid "Idha panāvuso, bhikkhu evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "Take another mendicant who says: "

msgctxt "dn34:94.2"
msgid "‘upekkhā hi kho me cetovimutti bhāvitā …"
