msgctxt "dn34:94.8"
msgid "nissaraṇaṃ hetaṃ, āvuso, rāgassa yadidaṃ upekkhācetovimuttī’ti."
msgstr ""
"For it is the heart’s release by equanimity that is the escape from desire.’"

msgctxt "dn34:94.9"
msgid "(7.4)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="87"></a>
msgctxt "dn34:95.1"
msgid "Idha panāvuso, bhikkhu evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "Take another mendicant who says:"

msgctxt "dn34:95.2"
msgid "‘animittā hi kho me cetovimutti bhāvitā …"
msgstr "‘I’ve developed the signless heart’s release. …"

msgctxt "dn34:95.3"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn34:95.4"
msgid "atha ca pana me nimittānusāri viññāṇaṃ hotī’ti."
msgstr "Yet somehow my consciousness still follows after signs.’"

msgctxt "dn34:95.5"
msgid "So:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn34:95.6"
msgid "‘mā hevan’tissa vacanīyo ‘māyasmā evaṃ avaca …"
